\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過主啦垃圾！</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做得好肥絲，無恥之徒必須追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3259b1f8b23131ccae41d7ee49a9c9f448be8bd","tid":470690,"uid":15860,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T14:21:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鴻福郎</span>──兩登牆頭草二五仔。連同其低劣笑話，齊名網絡垃圾，人人得而誅之</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">鴻福郎，於連登開壇時，高調由高登過檔。開post狂擦連登鞋，並大數高登不是，務求用出位言論於新論壇博得支持和人氣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/020057_0f2111fefbccef0b3f18b8b10464d669.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F020057_0f2111fefbccef0b3f18b8b10464d669.jpg&h=9800e8de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/020057_b0ccdf6ca3612021ceef9ad0f25589d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F020057_b0ccdf6ca3612021ceef9ad0f25589d1.jpg&h=8edf56fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後來，高登仔揭發連登已成立公司，由商業團體經營，並非大家所想的個人經營模式。同時，高登管理員為挽回流失的會員，大量解封違規會員。鴻福郎高調回歸高登並公開道歉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/020418_bde2632b17711201d77281d1a661ea2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F020418_bde2632b17711201d77281d1a661ea2d.jpg&h=74377a3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高登仔因不齒鴻福郎的牆頭草、唯利是圖的行為，眾人均稱他為「二五仔」，並趕他離開高登。鴻福郎為討好已得罪的高登仔，於高登不停開post攻擊連登，希望為自己的過失洗底。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/020418_af35b7ddd4cf581dc30a103a6c1a401c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F020418_af35b7ddd4cf581dc30a103a6c1a401c.jpg&h=091932f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/020417_af35b7ddd4cf581dc30a103a6c1a401c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F020417_af35b7ddd4cf581dc30a103a6c1a401c.jpg&h=d194575d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論鴻福郎有多盡力為自己洗底，都撇不掉自己在高登仔心目中的二五仔之名。鴻福郎便盡地一煲，於連登開post狂踩連登，並多番嘗試拉大隊返回高登。此舉與鴻福郎開壇時的行為大相逕庭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/022205_723a68ce26e1f26f960d5823c8310ae6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F022205_723a68ce26e1f26f960d5823c8310ae6.jpg&h=ac5575d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/022205_269651ac7a6a45128722170e00d2b4da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F022205_269651ac7a6a45128722170e00d2b4da.jpg&h=9987c5d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登仔對於鴻福郎的言論行為極度反感，紛紛喝他「過主」，鴻福郎卻繼續以囂張的態度繼續宣揚高登。另一方面，高登仔卻沒有因為鴻福郎的洗底行為而受落，繼續予以排斥。<br />\n<br />\n事隔大半年，兩登分裂已成定局，高登大勢已去。牆頭草鴻福郎後悔最初下錯決定，選了失勢的高登。現在兩邊不是人的他，於連登陰陰地開post發表他的垃圾笑話，希望連登仔能慢慢地習慣他的存在，再次接受他。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可是，鴻福郎，別妄想啦！人類對討厭的東西是不會善忘的，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過主啦垃圾！</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做得好肥絲，無恥之徒必須追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己ａｃ回？<br />\n郎郎死仆街回頭草～<br />\n<br />\nＳＯ　ＷＴ，你而家咪又要幫我推ｐｏ傻仔！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c2ab54e2bea1ab9c9bd3b19cd02a6030a03d4d","tid":470690,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鴻福郎</span>──兩登牆頭草二五仔。連同其低劣笑話，齊名網絡垃圾，人人得而誅之</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">鴻福郎，於連登開壇時，高調由高登過檔。開post狂擦連登鞋，並大數高登不是，務求用出位言論於新論壇博得支持和人氣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/020057_0f2111fefbccef0b3f18b8b10464d669.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F020057_0f2111fefbccef0b3f18b8b10464d669.jpg&h=9800e8de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/020057_b0ccdf6ca3612021ceef9ad0f25589d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F020057_b0ccdf6ca3612021ceef9ad0f25589d1.jpg&h=8edf56fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後來，高登仔揭發連登已成立公司，由商業團體經營，並非大家所想的個人經營模式。同時，高登管理員為挽回流失的會員，大量解封違規會員。鴻福郎高調回歸高登並公開道歉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/020418_bde2632b17711201d77281d1a661ea2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F020418_bde2632b17711201d77281d1a661ea2d.jpg&h=74377a3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高登仔因不齒鴻福郎的牆頭草、唯利是圖的行為，眾人均稱他為「二五仔」，並趕他離開高登。鴻福郎為討好已得罪的高登仔，於高登不停開post攻擊連登，希望為自己的過失洗底。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/020418_af35b7ddd4cf581dc30a103a6c1a401c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F020418_af35b7ddd4cf581dc30a103a6c1a401c.jpg&h=091932f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/020417_af35b7ddd4cf581dc30a103a6c1a401c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F020417_af35b7ddd4cf581dc30a103a6c1a401c.jpg&h=d194575d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論鴻福郎有多盡力為自己洗底，都撇不掉自己在高登仔心目中的二五仔之名。鴻福郎便盡地一煲，於連登開post狂踩連登，並多番嘗試拉大隊返回高登。此舉與鴻福郎開壇時的行為大相逕庭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/022205_723a68ce26e1f26f960d5823c8310ae6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F022205_723a68ce26e1f26f960d5823c8310ae6.jpg&h=ac5575d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/022205_269651ac7a6a45128722170e00d2b4da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F022205_269651ac7a6a45128722170e00d2b4da.jpg&h=9987c5d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登仔對於鴻福郎的言論行為極度反感，紛紛喝他「過主」，鴻福郎卻繼續以囂張的態度繼續宣揚高登。另一方面，高登仔卻沒有因為鴻福郎的洗底行為而受落，繼續予以排斥。<br />\n<br />\n事隔大半年，兩登分裂已成定局，高登大勢已去。牆頭草鴻福郎後悔最初下錯決定，選了失勢的高登。現在兩邊不是人的他，於連登陰陰地開post發表他的垃圾笑話，希望連登仔能慢慢地習慣他的存在，再次接受他。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可是，鴻福郎，別妄想啦！人類對討厭的東西是不會善忘的，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過主啦垃圾！</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做得好肥絲，無恥之徒必須追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己ａｃ回？<br />\n郎郎死仆街回頭草～<br />\n<br />\nＳＯ　ＷＴ，你而家咪又要幫我推ｐｏ傻仔！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁無恥，推到你隻老鼠人人喊打就必須啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1a373db9801919658075dd626323d6c1c1e613","tid":470690,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,